{"tid":851820,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【瘋狂大劈價】金獅花園420萬成交 低市價兩成","createTime":"2018-10-07T12:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T02:40:54.000Z","uid":83582,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb362b1a54ec760c2da095d1d25e30c50f1de65","tid":851820,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:15:12.000Z","msg":"2018年10月07日<br />\n<br />\n【瘋狂大劈價】金獅花園420萬成交 低市價兩成<br />\n<br />\n細價樓跌勢持續，不少上車屋苑造價已打回原形，重返年初價。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，大圍金獅花園剛錄得一宗瘋狂劈價成交。金麗閣中層4室，實用面積270方呎，上月中放盤，叫價480萬元，放盤近一個月，出貨艱難，大劈價至420萬元終沽出，呎價15,556元，撇除內部轉讓及凶宅後，造價創屋苑今年2月後的半年新低。樓市未回調前，即大約兩至三個前，金獅花園同類造價高達500萬元，其中金豐閣中層5室，實用面積260方呎，今年8月以510萬元售出，呎價19,615元。今次最新成交，呎價短短兩個月下調達兩成。<br />\n<br />\n代理表示，其實金獅花園年初時的造價也是400萬左右，只是在2月份過後，全城瘋搶細價樓，「那時的樓市是越細越貴」，現在跌兩成，只是回到較理性水平，期間升幅被蒸發。<br />\n<br />\n記者:朱連峰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181007/large/1538908633_693a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181007%2Flarge%2F1538908633_693a.jpg&h=9d0a9870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181007/58767563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181007%2F58767563&d=4xkOgrXO0dUXB3S%2FBHQ4HW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5ada7d78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181007%2F58767563&h=6132b67c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181007/58767563</a>"},{"pid":"91445c283ef04de35948c7352eec327f8e646d5c","tid":851820,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:20:56.000Z","msg":"無事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69252bfd194263d012d5120cb5ce2586fd25931","tid":8